{"tid":1298461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【耐人尋味】TVB突然取消DSE打氣活動 考生失望問點解","createTime":"2019-07-09T01:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:29:28.000Z","uid":19552,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c5e7400cd4c4e25b0e0598d9745e80d06a68a9","tid":1298461,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:35:33.000Z","msg":"TVB原本於今日（9日）在apm舉行「DSE考生-放榜前的一個晚上」安排藝人與歌手為考生打氣，昨日突然在TVB的facebook宣布取消：「由於節目調動, big big channel原訂2019年7月9日晚上8時的 &ldquo;放榜前的一個晚上&rdquo;將會取消。不便之處,敬請見諒。」據知活動原本邀陳柏宇、關楚耀、麥明詩、馮盈盈、ToNick、王灝兒（JW）、Super Girls等出席，眾嘉賓昨日臨時接獲通知活動取消，並不清楚原因。<br />\n<br />\n有網民留言問點解？有表示失望，寫道：「我哋成班應屆DSE生而家都唔知點 好大壓力呀！」又有指TVB要給考生一個交代。不過，有網民問是否跟有團體發起「反紅媒遊行」有關？有人和應指DSE打氣活動年年都搞，突然取消有此地無銀之嫌。"},{"pid":"ce8a36ee872902835b7cb27772b73e3e0b3743f1","tid":1298461,"uid":42217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:37:54.000Z","msg":"咩係TVB? 只係聽過CCTVB 中央電視台(香港)"},{"pid":"bbfe57392c15382c363459df3eef1ad1a38718f7","tid":1298461,"uid":29842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲照出APM?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53e0b05745f5af47d7eabde37dfe30ea25614ef","tid":1298461,"uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:03:08.000Z","msg":"因為知道成個台開始被人針對"},{"pid":"a840f2f6ffd98d3649a3a5fe43e8a5bd6634d04f","tid":1298461,"uid":72431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:04:24.000Z","msg":"我地都係dse考生<br />\n好大壓力<br />\n取消活動搞到我更大壓力<br />\n一齊投訴tbb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2af09003a416a0293010a20a4ccba9741556ca","tid":1298461,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbfe57392c15382c363459df3eef1ad1a38718f7","tid":1298461,"uid":29842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲照出APM?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"屌緊係照出<br />\n一襯冇人即刻再搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}